<td data-valign="top" width="468"><h3 id="chapter-4" data-align="center">CHAPTER 4</h3>
<h3 id="auto-suggestion" data-align="center">AUTO-SUGGESTION</h3>
<p>THE MEDIUM FOR INFLUENCING THE SUBCONSCIOUS MIND</p>
<p><em>The Third Step toward Riches</em></p></td>
<td width="71"><p><span id="img_rbrk"></span> <img src="img/rbrk.jpg" /></p></td>
</tr>
