<td data-valign="top"><p>Repeat this program night and morning until you can see, (in your imagination) the money you intend to accumulate.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td data-valign="top"><p>Third.</p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p>Place a written copy of your statement where you can see it night and morning, and read it just before retiring, and upon arising until it has been memorized.</p></td>
